value: 8221 - Colleges, Universities and Professional Schools Summary > THE ROYAL AUSTRALIAN AND NEW ZEALAND COLLEGE OF OBSTETRICIANS AND GYNAECOLOGISTS is an Australian public company. Its operations cover colleges, universities and professional schools. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. THE ROYAL AUSTRALIAN AND NEW ZEALAND COLLEGE OF OBSTETRICIANS AND GYNAECOLOGISTS is headquartered in Melbourne, Victoria. It is headed by chief executive officer Penelope Frances Griffits. For the 2025 financial year, the company reported revenue of $41.52 million. Its net profit totalled $816,000. THE ROYAL AUSTRALIAN AND NEW ZEALAND COLLEGE OF OBSTETRICIANS AND GYNAECOLOGISTS forms part of the services industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
